rows.label: bf04110100_0040
rows.name:
I'm sorry.
Hikari-chan has a habit of 
wandering around when she's half-asleep...

rows.label: bf04110100_0060
rows.name: She didn't do anything strange, did she?

rows.label: bf04110100_0070
rows.name:
No! I didn't do anything weird!
Not a thing!

rows.label: bf04110100_0080
rows.name:
No, that's not what I meant. 
I was asking about Hikari-chan.

rows.label: bf04110100_0100
rows.name:
Well...
She just threw some things at me, that's all.

rows.label: bf04110100_0110
rows.name: So that was where that came from.

rows.label: bf04110100_0120
rows.name:
I'm sorry.
It must have hurt, right?

rows.label: bf04110100_0130
rows.name:
N-no! It's okay!
Really, I'm fine!

rows.label: bf04110100_0140
rows.name:
Is that so?
My head is still throbbing a bit though...

rows.label: bf04110100_0150
rows.name: Youth is a wonderful thing, isn't it?

rows.label: bf04110100_0170
rows.name: I wish I had a girlfriend too...

rows.label: bf04110100_0180
rows.name: No, I'm quite fine, thank you...
